{"tid":2122551,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【重溫】「藏有工具可作非法用途」既「非法用途」，只限三種場景","createTime":"2020-07-24T05:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T11:47:54.000Z","uid":88743,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e9dcd40cf225e054fc2070885581ec3d52339259","tid":2122551,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"【抗暴一年】反修例案件定罪率僅49% 濫告管有非法工具成「新萬能key」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200611/OVHV3OMAUEF4ITTONDAW62BIEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200611%2FOVHV3OMAUEF4ITTONDAW62BIEA%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6IgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=516a930b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200611%2FOVHV3OMAUEF4ITTONDAW62BIEA%2F&h=12720279\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200611/OVHV3OMAUEF4ITTONDAW62BIEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6sdOkk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6sdOkk.gif&h=2a880ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《簡易程序治罪條例》第17條，根據案例，「非法用途」只限三種場景，包括是<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">傷人、束縛他人及闖入處所</span></span></strong>，且有半年起訴期限。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日竟然俾我見到格黎個ＰＯ<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">【大三罷】18歲生認藏六角匙 嚴舜儀考慮判監 需還押至8月7日判刑</span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fJuboS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fJuboS</a><br />\n<br />\n求情時，辯方先指被告剛成年，指被告涉案時間短、有真誠悔意，案發時遭警員喝停，沒有令任何人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母垃圾律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開名啦邊撚個辯護呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9